Get lat lon (and NAICS) via Facility Registry ID

Source: R/latlon_from_regid.R
latlon_from_regid.Rd

Get lat lon (and NAICS) via Facility Registry ID

Usage

latlon_from_regid(regid)

Arguments

regid

Facility Registry Service ID like 110010052520

Value

data.table with columns lat,lon,REGISTRY_ID,PRIMARY_NAME,NAICS,PGM_SYS_ACRNMS

Examples

 latlon_from_regid(110070874073)
#> Key: <REGISTRY_ID>
#>        lat       lon  REGISTRY_ID PRIMARY_NAME  NAICS    SIC  PGM_SYS_ACRNMS
#>      <num>     <num>       <char>       <char> <char> <char>          <char>
#> 1: 33.6611 -117.8696 110070874073    EJAM INC.               ICIS:3601252181
x = latlon_from_regid(
    c(110071293460, 110070874073, 110070538057, 110044340807,
       110030509215, 110019033810, 110056111559, 110056982323)
        )
